{"tid":1725832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百特別任務警宣誓 穿懲教服 肩章列身分","createTime":"2019-11-16T01:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:35:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b101941c20be64cbe82279440209dc726f19fa7e","tid":1725832,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:42:46.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】警務處長前日委任近100名懲教人員擔任「特別任務警察」，警方稱該批人員昨早已宣誓，未來數天會接受基本訓練。警方亦說，該批懲教人員執勤時會穿上懲教制服，肩章會用中英寫明是特別任務警察，但因涉及行動細節，未能披露執勤詳情。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司謝振中昨表示，有關的懲教人員已完成宣誓，警方會提供基本訓練，並會帶他們熟悉實地環境工作。他說，該批懲教人員執勤時會穿上懲教制服，膊頭有肩章，會用中英清晰寫明是特務警察，公眾可識別。被問有關人員未來工作地點、會否參與前線行動，謝則以涉行動細節為由未能披露詳情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191116/s00001/1573843798946/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191116%2Fs00001%2F1573843798946%2F&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=19e52f6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191116%2Fs00001%2F1573843798946%2F&h=f9250270\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191116/s00001/1573843798946/</a>"},{"pid":"24e7eef90d798d29c36c213cf57e2080dc6d61f6","tid":1725832,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba968a9b50296eb08ca825dbcf3a90e24ef2874","tid":1725832,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7159d70f4e083a77fbfec22e9073d7fdcb29a4","tid":1725832,"uid":148332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"點解要戴特別章？其中一個原因係想示威者見到佢地輕手d。<br />\n所以記得要照當佢地普通狗，唔洗可憐佢地"},{"pid":"a4cfc332c41b484d0601efe27ec2f003fd7ef2fb","ti